high_descs: Turn left and walk over to the couch.
Pick up the set of keys off of the couch.
Turn left and walk over to the chair with the newspaper on its seat.
Put the keys on the seat of the chair in front of the newspaper.
Turn left and walk forward, the hang a left and walk up to the wooden table with the television on it.
Pick up the set of keys off of the wooden table.
Turn left and walk forward, the hang a left and walk over to the chair on the other side of the room.
Put the keys to the right of the other keys on the seat of the chair.
anns.task_desc: Move two sets of keys to the seat of a chair.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the right side of the couch.
Pick up the keys from the couch.
Walk over to the brown chair to the left of the couch.
Put the keys down on the chair in front of the newspaper.
Walk over to the television stand.
Pick up the keys to the right of the remote.
Walk back over to the brown chair.
Put the keys down to the right of the other keys on the brown chair.
anns.task_desc: To move two sets of keys to the brown chair.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the black couch.
Pick up the set of keys from the right side of the couch.
Turn left and walk to the black chair.
Put the set of keys on the chair in front of the newspaper.
Turn left and walk to the television stand to the left.
Pick up the set of keys from the right corner of the stand.
Turn around and walk to the black chair.
Put the set of keys on the chair to the right of the other set of keys.
anns.task_desc: Place two sets of keys on a chair.
